                <div class="result-inner-box">
                    <span class="bold">F&#246;rordning (1994:522) om f&#246;rm&#229;ner till instrukt&#246;rer inom frivillig f&#246;rsvarsutbildning</span>
                </div>

                
                <div class="result-inner-box">
                    <span class="bold">Departement:</span> F&#246;rsvarsdepartementet
                </div>
                
                <div class="result-inner-box">
                    <span class="bold">Utfärdad:</span> 1994-05-19
                </div>
                
                <div class="result-inner-box">
                    <span class="bold">Ändring införd:</span> t.o.m. SFS 2018:201
                </div>
                
                <div class="result-inner-box">
                    <span class="bold">Ikraft:</span> 1994-07-01
